									<li>A cybersecurity event at the Nord Franche-Comté IUT with a solo CTF competition which I won.</li>
								</div>

						</div>
					</div>

				</div>		
			</section>
			<div style="margin-bottom: 60px;"></div>
		</main>

	</div>
</BaseLayout>

